sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant PaymentGateway as Payment Gateway
    participant Database as Transaction Database
    participant Compliance as Compliance System

    User->>App: Initiate Payment/P2P Transfer
    App->>PaymentGateway: Process Payment
    PaymentGateway-->>App: Payment Confirmation
    App->>Database: Record Transaction
    Database-->>App: Transaction Recorded
    App->>User: Show Payment Confirmation

    User->>App: Request Transaction History
    App->>Database: Retrieve Transaction History
    Database-->>App: Transaction History Data
    App->>User: Display Transaction History

    App->>Compliance: Verify Compliance
    Compliance-->>App: Compliance Check Passed